vision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(190,1,'2015-08-02 20:27:10','2015-08-02 12:27:10','<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-189\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/2-300x153.png\" alt=\"2\" width=\"300\" height=\"153\" /></a>','Android中使用的数据单位','','inherit','open','open','','188-revision-v1','','','2015-08-02 20:27:10','2015-08-02 12:27:10','',188,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/08/02/188-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(188,1,'2015-08-02 20:27:10','2015-08-02 12:27:10','<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-189\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/2-300x153.png\" alt=\"2\" width=\"300\" height=\"153\" /></a>','Android中使用的数据单位','','publish','open','open','','android%e4%b8%ad%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8%e7%9a%84%e6%95%b0%e6%8d%ae%e5%8d%95%e4%bd%8d','','','2015-08-02 20:27:10','2015-08-02 12:27:10','',0,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/?p=188',0,'post','',0),(68,1,'2015-07-21 16:22:07','2015-07-21 08:22:07','合并分支\r\n\r\n代码冲突\r\n\r\n解决方法','Git指南：（二）Git分支与合并','','inherit','open','open','','42-revision-v1','','','2015-07-21 16:22:07','2015-07-21 08:22:07','',42,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/21/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(65,1,'2015-07-20 09:02:48','2015-07-20 01:02:48','[hermit auto=\"1\" loop=\"1\" unexpand=\"0\"]remote#:1[/hermit]新建分支\r\n\r\n合并分支\r\n\r\n代码冲突\r\n\r\n解决方法','2-Git分支与合并','','inherit','open','open','','42-revision-v1','','','2015-07-20 09:02:48','2015-07-20 01:02:48','',42,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/20/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(69,1,'2015-07-21 16:24:36','2015-07-21 08:24:36','<h2>一、简介</h2>\r\n<b>Nginx</b>是一款轻量级的Web 服务器/反向代理服务器及电子邮件（IMAP/POP3）代理服务器，并在一个BSD-like 协议下发行。由俄罗斯的程序设计师Igor Sysoev所开发，供俄国大型的入口网站及搜索引擎Rambler（俄文：Рамблер）使用。其特点是占有内存少，并发能力强，事实上nginx的并发能力确实在同类型的网页服务器中表现较好，中国大陆使用nginx网站用户有：百度、新浪、腾讯等。\r\n<h2>二、安装</h2>\r\n<h3>①yum安装</h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">（以CentOS为例）</span>\r\n<h4>1、添加yum源：</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">(1)在/etc/yum.repos.d/目录下新建一个yum源文件nginx.repo：</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;\">cd /etc/yum.repos.d/</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;\">touch nginx.repo</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;\">vi nginx.repo</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">(2)将下面的内容复制进去。</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">[nginx]</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">name=nginx repo</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">baseurl=http://nginx.org/packages/centos/$releasever/$basearch/</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">gpgcheck=0</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">enabled=1</div>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<h4>2、使用命令查看是否成功：</h4>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">yum list | grep nginx</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-51\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum-300x188.png\" alt=\"lnmp_nginx_yum\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" /></a></div>\r\n结果如图就是成功了！\r\n<h4>3、使用yum命令安装：</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">yum install nginx</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_install.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-52\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_install-300x296.png\" alt=\"lnmp_nginx_yum_install\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">如图就表示安装完成且成功了！</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>4、启动服务</h4>\r\n命令如下：\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">/etc/rc.d/init.d/nginx start</p>\r\n<strong>或</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">service nginx start</p>\r\n<strong>PS:</strong>\r\n\r\n停止nginx服务：/etc/rc.d/init.d/nginx stop\r\n\r\n重启nginx服务：/etc/rc.d/init.d/nginx restart\r\n\r\n设置开机自动启动：chkconfig nginx on\r\n\r\n查看网络监听：netstat -lntp | grep nginx\r\n<h4>5、其他</h4>\r\n(1)nginx的配置文件在：<strong>/etc/nginx/nginx.conf</strong>\r\n\r\n(2)可以使用命令查看自己感兴趣的东西：\r\n\r\n如：\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">whereis nginx</p>\r\n结果：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_whereis.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-53\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_whereis-300x35.png\" alt=\"lnmp_nginx_yum_whereis\" width=\"300\" height=\"35\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n==========================================================================================================\r\n<h3>②源代码安装</h3>','Ngiex服务器（一）--安装','','inherit','open','open','','30-revision-v1','','','2015-07-21 16:24:36','2015-07-21 08:24:36','',30,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/21/30-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(70,1,'2015-07-21 16:26:25','2015-07-21 08:26:25','<strong>Android动画分为如下4种：</strong>\r\n\r\n①TweenAnimation：转换动画\r\n\r\n②LayoutAnimation：布局动画\r\n\r\n③FrameAnimation：帧动画\r\n\r\n④PropertyAnimation：属性动画\r\n<h6>转换动画又分为4种：</h6>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>AlphaAnimation</li>\r\n	<li>ScaleAnimation</li>\r\n	<li>TranslateAnimation</li>\r\n	<li>RotateAnimation</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n有了TweenAnimation、LayoutAnimation、FrameAnimation，为什么谷歌还有提供PropertyAnimation呢？这是因为。。。。。。其中一种情况是，你对某个View写了点击事件，但是当它执行TranslateAnimation动画后，你再点击它就不能触发它的点击事件了，你得在他原来的位置点击才能触发其点击事件。\r\n\r\nsemi 于 二〇一五年七月十三日 18:35:34','Android动画（一）','','inherit','open','open','','24-revision-v1','','','2015-07-21 16:26:25','2015-07-21 08:26:25','',24,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/21/24-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(71,1,'2015-07-21 16:29:27','2015-07-21 08:29:27','TweenAnimation变换动画共有4种：\n<ol>\n	<li>透明度渐变动画（AlphaAnimation）</li>\n	<li>尺寸缩放动画（ScaleAnimation）</li>\n	<li>位置移动动画（TranslateAnimation）</li>\n	<li>旋转动画（RotateAnimation）。</li>\n</ol>\n所有变换动画共有的属性有：\n<ol>\n	<li>duration：动画持续时间</li>\n	<li>fillAfter：设置为true，则在动画结束后保持不变。如位置移动动画，则是动画结束后，移动到哪了，就在那，而不回原位置。</li>\n	<li>fillBefore：这个我也不知道（<strong><em>待补充</em></strong>）。</li>\n	<li>interpolator：动画插入器，如先匀速再加速最后减速等。</li>\n	<li>repeatCount：重复次数。</li>\n	<li>repeatMode：重复模式，RESTART顺序，REVERSR倒序。</li>\n	<li>startOffset：动画开始前的时间间隔。可用于由两个动画组成的组合动画，例如A动画播放3秒，想要B动画在A动画之后紧接着开始播放，则把B动画的startOffset设为3秒。</li>\n</ol>\n对这4种变换动画，现分别介绍如下：\n\n一、AlphaAnimation\n\n①JAVA代码实现：\n\nImageView imageView = (ImageView)findViewById(R.id.img);//查找ImageView\n\nAnimation anim = new AlphaAnimation(0.2f , 1.0f);//创建一个AlphaAnimation动画对象\n\nanim.setDuration(5000);//5s\n\nImageView.startAnimation(alpha);\n\n②资源文件（/res/anim）：alpha_anim.xml\n\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" ?&gt;\n\n&lt;set xmlns:android=\"http://schema.android.com/apl/res/android\"&gt;\n\n&lt;alpha\n\nandroid:duration=\"2000\"\n\nandroid:fromAlpha=\"0.2\"\n\nandroid:toAlpha=\"1.0\"/&gt;\n\n&lt;/set&gt;\n\nAlphaAnimation alphaAnim = AnimationUtils.loadAnimation(上下文 , R.anim.alpha_anim);//使用AnimationUtils工具类来加载动画文件\n\n二、ScaleAnimation\n\nImageView imageView = (ImageView)findViewById(R.id.img);//查找ImageView\n\nAnimation anim = new ScaleAnimation();','Android动画（二）--TweenAnimation','','inherit','open','open','','26-autosave-v1','','','2015-07-21 16:29:27','2015-07-21 08:29:27','',26,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/21/26-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(72,1,'2015-07-21 16:30:43','2015-07-21 08:30:43','TweenAnimation变换动画共有4种：\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>透明度渐变动画（AlphaAnimation）</li>\r\n	<li>尺寸缩放动画（ScaleAnimation）</li>\r\n	<li>位置移动动画（TranslateAnimation）</li>\r\n	<li>旋转动画（RotateAnimation）。</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n所有变换动画共有的属性有：\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>duration：动画持续时间</li>\r\n	<li>fillAfter：设置为true，则在动画结束后保持不变。如位置移动动画，则是动画结束后，移动到哪了，就在那，而不回原位置。</li>\r\n	<li>fillBefore：这个我也不知道（<strong><em>待补充</em></strong>）。</li>\r\n	<li>interpolator：动画插入器，如先匀速再加速最后减速等。</li>\r\n	<li>repeatCount：重复次数。</li>\r\n	<li>repeatMode：重复模式，RESTART顺序，REVERSR倒序。</li>\r\n	<li>startOffset：动画开始前的时间间隔。可用于由两个动画组成的组合动画，例如A动画播放3秒，想要B动画在A动画之后紧接着开始播放，则把B动画的startOffset设为3秒。</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n对这4种变换动画，现分别介绍如下：\r\n<h3>一、AlphaAnimation</h3>\r\n①纯JAVA代码实现：\r\n\r\nImageView imageView = (ImageView)findViewById(R.id.img);//查找ImageView\r\n\r\nAnimation anim = new AlphaAnimation(0.2f , 1.0f);//创建一个AlphaAnimation动画对象\r\n\r\nanim.setDuration(5000);//5s\r\n\r\nImageView.startAnimation(alpha);\r\n\r\n②资源文件+JAVA代码（/res/anim）：\r\n\r\n<strong>alpha_anim.xml：</strong>\r\n\r\n&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" ?&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;set xmlns:android=\"http://schema.android.com/apl/res/android\"&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;alpha\r\n\r\nandroid:duration=\"2000\"\r\n\r\nandroid:fromAlpha=\"0.2\"\r\n\r\nandroid:toAlpha=\"1.0\"/&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/set&gt;\r\n\r\n<strong>JAVA代码：</strong>\r\n\r\nAlphaAnimation alphaAnim = AnimationUtils.loadAnimation(上下文 , R.anim.alpha_anim);//使用AnimationUtils工具类来加载动画文件\r\n<h3>二、ScaleAnimation</h3>\r\nImageView imageView = (ImageView)findViewById(R.id.img);//查找ImageView\r\n\r\nAnimation anim = new ScaleAnimation();','Android动画（二）--TweenAnimation','','inherit','open','open','','26-revision-v1','','','2015-07-21 16:30:43','2015-07-21 08:30:43','',26,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/21/26-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(73,1,'2015-07-21 16:31:38','2015-07-21 08:31:38','','Android动画（三）--LayoutAnimation','','publish','open','open','','android%e5%8a%a8%e7%94%bb%ef%bc%88%e4%b8%89%ef%bc%89-layoutanimation','','','2015-07-21 16:31:38','2015-07-21 08:31:38','',0,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/?p=73',0,'post','',0),(74,1,'2015-07-21 16:31:38','2015-07-21 08:31:38','','Android动画（三）--LayoutAnimation','','inherit','open','open','','73-revision-v1','','','2015-07-21 16:31:38','2015-07-21 08:31:38','',73,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/21/73-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(75,1,'2015-07-21 16:32:02','2015-07-21 08:32:02','','Android动画（四）--FrameAnimation','','publish','open','open','','android%e5%8a%a8%e7%94%bb%ef%bc%88%e5%9b%9b%ef%bc%89-frameanimation','','','2015-07-21 16:32:02','2015-07-21 08:32:02','',0,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/?p=75',0,'post','',0),(76,1,'2015-07-21 16:32:02','2015-07-21 08:32:02','','Android动画（四）--FrameAnimation','','inherit','open','open','','75-revision-v1','','','2015-07-21 16:32:02','2015-07-21 08:32:02','',75,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/21/75-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(77,1,'2015-07-21 16:32:25','2015-07-21 08:32:25','','Android动画（五）--PropertyAnimation','','publish','open','open','','android%e5%8a%a8%e7%94%bb%ef%bc%88%e4%ba%94%ef%bc%89-propertyanimation','','','2015-07-21 16:32:25','2015-07-21 08:32:25','',0,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/?p=77',0,'post','',0),(78,1,'2015-07-21 16:32:25','2015-07-21 08:32:25','','Android动画（五）--PropertyAnimation','','inherit','open','open','','77-revision-v1','','','2015-07-21 16:32:25','2015-07-21 08:32:25','',77,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/21/77-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(80,1,'2015-07-23 19:06:00','2015-07-23 11:06:00','一、综述\r\n\r\nsplash =&gt; 引导页 =&gt; 主界面\r\n\r\nsplash和引导页在启动下一个Activity的时候，记得要调用finish()来结束当前Activity，因为他们都不在使用了。\r\n\r\n二、splash\r\n\r\n由一个Activity自动启动另一个Activity是使用handle来实现。\r\n\r\nnew Handle().postDelayed(new Runnabel(){\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Intent intent = new Intent(---,---);</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">startActivity(intent);</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">this.finish();</p>\r\n},3000);','Android App 开发起步','','inherit','open','open','','79-revision-v1','','','2015-07-23 19:06:00','2015-07-23 11:06:00','',79,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/23/79-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(162,1,'2015-07-31 16:05:36','2015-07-31 08:05:36','1、设置值：\r\n<pre>$_SESSION[\"XXX\"] = XXX;</pre>\r\n2、删除单个值：\r\n<pre>unset($_SESSION[\"xxx\"]);</pre>\r\n3、检查某个SESSION值是否存在：\r\n<pre>isset($_SESSION[\"xxx\"]);  //返回bool</pre>\r\n4、结束会话：\r\n<pre>session_destroy() ;</pre>\r\n结束当前的会话，并清空会话中的所有资源。该函数不会 unset (释放)和当前 session 相关的全局变量(globalvariables)，也不会删除客户端的 session cookie。\r\n\r\nPHP 默认的 session 是基于 cookie 的，如果要删除 cookie 的话，必须借助 setcookie() 函数。返回值：布尔值。功能说明：这个函数结束当前的 session，此函数没有参数，且返回值均为 true。\r\n\r\n+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++\r\n\r\n下面是 PHP 官方关于删除 session 的案例：\r\n<pre>&lt;?php\r\n//初始化session\r\nsession_start();\r\n\r\n//删除所有的session变量\r\n//也可以用unset($_SESSION[\"xxx\"])的方式逐个删除\r\n$_SESSION = array();  //置为空数组\r\n\r\n//删除系统定义的session id(既是PHPSESSID)，由于默认是基于\r\n//cookie的，所有要使用setcookie(xxx)删除包含session id的cookie。\r\nif(isset($_COOKIE[\"PHPSESSID\"])){\r\n     setcookie(\"PHPSESSID\",\"\",time()-1,\"/\");\r\n     //从跟目录开始，马上过期\r\n}\r\n?&gt;</pre>\r\n由此我们可以得出删除Session的步骤：\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>session_start();</li>\r\n	<li>$_SESSION=array()或unset($_SESSION[''xxx''])</li>\r\n	<li>session_destroy()</li>\r\n</ol>','PHP:Session','','publish','open','open','','phpsession','','','2015-07-31 17:27:19','2015-07-31 09:27:19','',0,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/?p=162',0,'post','',0),(82,1,'2015-07-23 19:06:57','2015-07-23 11:06:57','Android ViewPager','Android ViewPager','','publish','open','open','','android-viewpager','','','2015-07-23 19:06:57','2015-07-23 11:06:57','',0,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/?p=82',0,'post','',0),(83,1,'2015-07-23 19:06:57','2015-07-23 11:06:57','Android ViewPager','Android ViewPager','','inherit','open','open','','82-revision-v1','','','2015-07-23 19:06:57','2015-07-23 11:06:57','',82,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/23/82-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(84,1,'2015-07-25 15:34:53','2015-07-25 07:34:53','','0','','inherit','open','open','','0','','','2015-07-25 15:34:53','2015-07-25 07:34:53','',30,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/0.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(85,1,'2015-07-25 15:45:18','2015-07-25 07:45:18','','1','','inherit','open','open','','1','','','2015-07-25 15:45:18','2015-07-25 07:45:18','',30,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(86,1,'2015-07-25 15:46:01','2015-07-25 07:46:01','<h2>一、简介</h2>\r\n<b>Nginx</b>是一款轻量级的Web 服务器/反向代理服务器及电子邮件（IMAP/POP3）代理服务器，并在一个BSD-like 协议下发行。由俄罗斯的程序设计师Igor Sysoev所开发，供俄国大型的入口网站及搜索引擎Rambler（俄文：Рамблер）使用。其特点是占有内存少，并发能力强，事实上nginx的并发能力确实在同类型的网页服务器中表现较好，中国大陆使用nginx网站用户有：百度、新浪、腾讯等。\r\n<h2>二、安装</h2>\r\n<h3>①yum安装</h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">（以CentOS为例）</span>\r\n<h4>1、添加yum源：</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">(1)在/etc/yum.repos.d/目录下新建一个yum源文件nginx.repo：</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;\">cd /etc/yum.repos.d/</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;\">touch nginx.repo</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;\">vi nginx.repo</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">(2)将下面的内容复制进去。</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">[nginx]</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">name=nginx repo</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">baseurl=http://nginx.org/packages/centos/$releasever/$basearch/</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">gpgcheck=0</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">enabled=1</div>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<h4>2、使用命令查看是否成功：</h4>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">yum list | grep nginx</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-51\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum-300x188.png\" alt=\"lnmp_nginx_yum\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" /></a></div>\r\n结果如图就是成功了！\r\n<h4>3、使用yum命令安装：</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">yum install nginx</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_install.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-52\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_install-300x296.png\" alt=\"lnmp_nginx_yum_install\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">如图就表示安装完成且成功了！</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>4、启动服务</h4>\r\n命令如下：\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">/etc/rc.d/init.d/nginx start</p>\r\n<strong>或</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">service nginx start</p>\r\n<strong>PS:</strong>\r\n\r\n停止nginx服务：/etc/rc.d/init.d/nginx stop\r\n\r\n重启nginx服务：/etc/rc.d/init.d/nginx restart\r\n\r\n设置开机自动启动：chkconfig nginx on\r\n\r\n查看网络监听：netstat -lntp | grep nginx\r\n<h4>5、其他</h4>\r\n(1)nginx的配置文件在：<strong>/etc/nginx/nginx.conf</strong>\r\n\r\n(2)可以使用命令查看自己感兴趣的东西：\r\n\r\n如：\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">whereis nginx</p>\r\n结果：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_whereis.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-53\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_whereis-300x35.png\" alt=\"lnmp_nginx_yum_whereis\" width=\"300\" height=\"35\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n==========================================================\r\n<h3>②源代码安装</h3>\r\n1、下载Nginx源码\r\n\r\n（1）先获取下载链接，再使用wget命令下载Nginx源码：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/0.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-84\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/0-300x240.png\" alt=\"0\" width=\"300\" height=\"240\" /></a>\r\n\r\n例如：wget http://nginx.org/download/nginx-1.8.0.tar.gz\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-85\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/1-300x126.png\" alt=\"1\" width=\"300\" height=\"126\" /></a>\r\n\r\n（2）编译源码并安装','Ngiex服务器（一）--安装','','inherit','open','open','','30-revision-v1','','','2015-07-25 15:46:01','2015-07-25 07:46:01','',30,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/25/30-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(87,1,'2015-07-25 15:49:59','2015-07-25 07:49:59','','2','','inherit','open','open','','2','','','2015-07-25 15:49:59','2015-07-25 07:49:59','',30,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(88,1,'2015-07-25 15:50:14','2015-07-25 07:50:14','','3','','inherit','open','open','','3','','','2015-07-25 15:50:14','2015-07-25 07:50:14','',30,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(89,1,'2015-07-25 15:59:37','2015-07-25 07:59:37','<h2>一、简介</h2>\r\n<b>Nginx</b>是一款轻量级的Web 服务器/反向代理服务器及电子邮件（IMAP/POP3）代理服务器，并在一个BSD-like 协议下发行。由俄罗斯的程序设计师Igor Sysoev所开发，供俄国大型的入口网站及搜索引擎Rambler（俄文：Рамблер）使用。其特点是占有内存少，并发能力强，事实上nginx的并发能力确实在同类型的网页服务器中表现较好，中国大陆使用nginx网站用户有：百度、新浪、腾讯等。\r\n<h2>二、安装</h2>\r\n<h3>①yum安装</h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">（以CentOS为例）</span>\r\n<h4>1、添加yum源：</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">(1)在/etc/yum.repos.d/目录下新建一个yum源文件nginx.repo：</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;\">cd /etc/yum.repos.d/</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;\">touch nginx.repo</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 60px;\">vi nginx.repo</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">(2)将下面的内容复制进去。</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">[nginx]</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">name=nginx repo</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">baseurl=http://nginx.org/packages/centos/$releasever/$basearch/</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">gpgcheck=0</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">enabled=1</div>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<h4>2、使用命令查看是否成功：</h4>\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">yum list | grep nginx</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-51\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum-300x188.png\" alt=\"lnmp_nginx_yum\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" /></a></div>\r\n结果如图就是成功了！\r\n<h4>3、使用yum命令安装：</h4>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">yum install nginx</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_install.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-52\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_install-300x296.png\" alt=\"lnmp_nginx_yum_install\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">如图就表示安装完成且成功了！</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>4、启动服务</h4>\r\n命令如下：\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">/etc/rc.d/init.d/nginx start</p>\r\n<strong>或</strong>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">service nginx start</p>\r\n<strong>PS:</strong>\r\n\r\n停止nginx服务：/etc/rc.d/init.d/nginx stop\r\n\r\n重启nginx服务：/etc/rc.d/init.d/nginx restart\r\n\r\n设置开机自动启动：chkconfig nginx on\r\n\r\n查看网络监听：netstat -lntp | grep nginx\r\n<h4>5、其他</h4>\r\n(1)nginx的配置文件在：<strong>/etc/nginx/nginx.conf</strong>\r\n\r\n(2)可以使用命令查看自己感兴趣的东西：\r\n\r\n如：\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">whereis nginx</p>\r\n结果：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_whereis.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-53\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/lnmp_nginx_yum_whereis-300x35.png\" alt=\"lnmp_nginx_yum_whereis\" width=\"300\" height=\"35\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n==========================================================\r\n<h3>②源代码安装</h3>\r\n1、下载Nginx源码\r\n\r\n（1）先获取下载链接，再使用wget命令下载Nginx源码：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/0.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-84\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/0-300x240.png\" alt=\"0\" width=\"300\" height=\"240\" /></a>\r\n\r\n例如：wget http://nginx.org/download/nginx-1.8.0.tar.gz\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-85\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/1-300x126.png\" alt=\"1\" width=\"300\" height=\"126\" /></a>\r\n\r\n（2）编译源码并安装\r\n\r\n如图，进入目录后执行： ./configure\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-87\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2-300x207.png\" alt=\"2\" width=\"300\" height=\"207\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-88\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/3-300x116.png\" alt=\"3\" width=\"300\" height=\"116\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n报错了，因为Nginx处理动态页面需要使用正则表达式，就需要pcre库的支持。\r\n\r\n除此之外，还需要gzip、gcc、gcc-c++的支持，所以在编译安装之前，先安装Nginx所需要的依赖。\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">yum install gcc gcc-c++ autoconf automake</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">yum install pcre pcre-devel</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">yum install zlib zlib-devel</span></p>\r\n当安装好这些依赖后就可以编译安装了\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">./configure</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">make</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">make install</span></p>','Ngiex服务器（一）--安装','','inherit','open','open','','30-revision-v1','','','2015-07-25 15:59:37','2015-07-25 07:59:37','',30,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/25/30-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(90,1,'2015-07-25 16:36:10','2015-07-25 08:36:10','<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">在<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/07/14/ngiex%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/\" target=\"_blank\">上一篇博文</a>中已经详细介绍了如何安装Nginx，现在开始安装Mysql和PHP。</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>一、安装Mysql</h3>\r\n（1）yum install mysql mysql-server\r\n\r\n其中mysql是mysql客户端和一些lib库，而mysql-server是mysql数据库服务器。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/13.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-91\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/13-300x209.png\" alt=\"13\" width=\"300\" height=\"209\" /></a>\r\n\r\n（2）启动mysql服务器，会自动完成一些初始化工作：\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/111.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-114\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/111-300x273.png\" alt=\"11\" width=\"300\" height=\"273\" /></a>\r\n\r\n（2）启动完成后，需要设置root用户的密码，有2种方式，分别介绍如下：\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">&lt;1&gt;/usr/bin/mysqladmin -u root password ''new-password''  或  /usr/bin/mysqladmin -u root -h DevMachine password ''new-password''</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">&lt;2&gt;使用：<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">mysql_secure_installation</span>命令,会提示设置root账户密码和删除test数据库和匿名用户等（当提示输入root用户密码时，因为没有密码，所有直接回车就可以了）。</p>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/mysql1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-116\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/mysql1-300x220.png\" alt=\"mysql1\" width=\"300\" height=\"220\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/mysql2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-117\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/mysql2-277x300.png\" alt=\"mysql2\" width=\"277\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n（3）启动mysqld服务：\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">/etc/rc.d/init.d/mysqld start</span></p>\r\n（4）mysql的配置文件在：/etc/my.cnf\r\n\r\n（5）到此，mysql已经安装完毕了，可以连接mysql服务器进行后续操作了。\r\n<h3>二、安装php</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/31.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-96\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/31-283x300.png\" alt=\"31\" width=\"283\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\n（1）需要先安装PHP\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 90px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">yum install php</span></p>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/32.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-97\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/32-300x175.png\" alt=\"32\" width=\"300\" height=\"175\" /></a>\r\n\r\n先使用yum命令安装php会因为解决而按照一部分组件。其他组件按需安装。\r\n\r\n（2）安装php的其他组件，如<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">php-mcrypt、php-mhash、 php-xml、php-mbstring、libjpeg*、php-pear等。</span>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">yum install php-mcrypt php-mhash php-xml php-mbstring libjpeg* php-pear</p>\r\n<b>&lt;1&gt;php-mcrypt：</b>PHP程序员们在编写代码程序时，除了要保证代码的高性能之外，还有一点是非常重要的，那就是程序的<b>安全性</b>保障。PHP除了自带的几种加密函数外，还有功能更全面的PHP加密扩展库<b>Mcrypt</b>和<b>Mhash</b>。\r\n\r\n其中，Mcrypt扩展库可以实现加密解密功能，就是既能将明文加密，也可以密文还原。\r\n\r\nmcrypt 是 php 里面重要的加密支持扩展库，linux环境下：该库在默认情况下不开启。window环境下：PHP&gt;=5.3,默认开启mcrypt扩展。\r\n\r\nMcrypt库支持20多种加密算法和8种加密模式，具体可以通过函数mcrypt_list_algorithms()和mcrypt_list_modes()来显示。\r\n\r\n<strong>&lt;2&gt;php-mhash：</strong>Mhash是基于<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/10467.htm\" target=\"_blank\">离散数学</a>原理的不可逆向的php加密方式扩展库，其在默认情况下不开启。mhash的可以用于创建校验数值，消息摘要，消息认证码，以及无需原文的关键信息保存（如密码）等。\r\n\r\nMhash为PHP提供了多种<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/99075.htm\" target=\"_blank\">哈希</a>算法，如<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/7636.htm\" target=\"_blank\">MD5</a>，<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/1228622.htm\" target=\"_blank\">SHA1</a>，<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/1110047.htm\" target=\"_blank\">GOST</a> 等。你可以通过<b>MHASH_hashname（）</b>来查看支持的算法有哪些。\r\n\r\n<strong>&lt;3&gt;php-pear：</strong>PEAR是PHP代码的仓库，在这里可以找到很多有用的代码，避免我们重复写一些功能，但是PEAR代码包并不是直接通过HTTP网站下载的，我们需要安装PEAR。\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/33.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-101\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/33-207x300.png\" alt=\"33\" width=\"207\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\n（3）php的配置文件在：/etc/php.ini\r\n<h3>三、使Nginx支持php</h3>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">cp /etc/nginx/nginx.conf /etc/nginx/nginx.conf.back</span>   #备份原有配置文件\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">vi /etc/nginx/nginx.conf  </span>   #修改配置文件</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">cp /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf.back</span>   #备份原有配置文件\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">vi /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf</span> #修改配置文件</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/00.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-105\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/00-244x300.png\" alt=\"00\" width=\"244\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>取消FastCGI server部分location的注释,并要注意fastcgi_param行的参数,改为$document_root$fastcgi_script_name,或者使用绝对路径。</strong></p>','LNMP安装','','publish','open','open','','lnmp%e5%ae%8