2 10:55:08','2015-10-02 02:55:08','','Apache 虚拟主机的配置','','inherit','open','open','','278-revision-v1','','','2015-10-02 10:55:08','2015-10-02 02:55:08','',278,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/10/02/278-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(280,1,'2015-10-02 11:09:39','2015-10-02 03:09:39','Apache虚拟主机的配置需要修改两个配置文件：httpd.conf、httpd-vhosts.conf。\n\n一、修改Apache主配置文件\n\nhttpd.conf的位置在\n\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/conf.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/conf-300x178.png\" alt=\"conf\" width=\"300\" height=\"178\" /></a>\n\n需要修改2个地方：\n\n①注释掉：\n\n#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n#DocumentRoot \"c:/Apache24/htdocs\"\n\n#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n②开启虚拟主机扩展：\n<pre>#------------------------------------------------------------\n# Virtual hosts\nInclude conf/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf\n#-------------------------------------------------------------</pre>\n二、配置虚拟主机\n\n编辑httpd-vhosts.conf配置文件，配置虚拟主机\n\n添加如下代码：\n<pre>&lt;VirtualHost *:90&gt;\n    DocumentRoot \"H:/runda/code/runda\"\n    ServerName www.runda.com\n    ServerAlias runda.com\n    ErrorLog \"logs/runda.log\"\n    CustomLog \"logs/runda-access.log\" common\n&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;\n&lt;Directory H:/runda/code/runda&gt;\n    Options FollowSymLinks\n    AllowOverride None\n    Order deny,allow\n    allow from all\n&lt;/Directory&gt;\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">注意：</span>\n\n</pre>\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;','Apache 虚拟主机的配置','','inherit','open','open','','278-autosave-v1','','','2015-10-02 11:09:39','2015-10-02 03:09:39','',278,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/10/02/278-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(281,1,'2015-10-02 11:02:58','2015-10-02 03:02:58','','conf','','inherit','open','open','','conf','','','2015-10-02 11:02:58','2015-10-02 03:02:58','',278,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/conf.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(282,1,'2015-10-02 11:11:06','2015-10-02 03:11:06','Apache虚拟主机的配置需要修改两个配置文件：httpd.conf、httpd-vhosts.conf。\r\n\r\n一、修改Apache主配置文件\r\n\r\nhttpd.conf的位置在\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/conf.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"http://www.ifuxs.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/conf-300x178.png\" alt=\"conf\" width=\"300\" height=\"178\" /></a>\r\n\r\n需要修改2个地方：\r\n\r\n①注释掉：\r\n\r\n#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n#DocumentRoot \"c:/Apache24/htdocs\"\r\n\r\n#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n②开启虚拟主机扩展：\r\n<pre>#------------------------------------------------------------\r\n# Virtual hosts\r\nInclude conf/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf\r\n#-------------------------------------------------------------</pre>\r\n二、配置虚拟主机\r\n\r\n编辑httpd-vhosts.conf配置文件，配置虚拟主机\r\n\r\n添加如下代码：\r\n<pre>&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;\r\n    DocumentRoot \"H:/runda/code/runda\"\r\n    ServerName www.runda.com\r\n    ServerAlias runda.com\r\n    ErrorLog \"logs/runda.log\"\r\n    CustomLog \"logs/runda-access.log\" common\r\n&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;\r\n&lt;Directory H:/runda/code/runda&gt;\r\n    Options FollowSymLinks\r\n    AllowOverride None\r\n    Order deny,allow\r\n    allow from all\r\n&lt;/Directory&gt;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">注意：\r\n①www.runda.com是虚拟主机的域名；\r\n②两部分是对应的，需要同时出现。</span></strong>\r\n三、完成。\r\n\r\n\r\nsemi 与2015年10月2日11:12:57</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Apache 虚拟主机的配置','','inherit','open','open','','278-revision-v1','','','2015-10-02 11:11:06','2015-10-02 03:11:06','',278,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/2015/10/02/278-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(284,1,'2015-10-10 21:54:16','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','自动草稿','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-10-10 21:54:16','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.ifuxs.cn/?p=284',0,'post','',0);
